{"tid":1945424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平回覆譚德塞 感謝世衛領導抗疫工作有方","createTime":"2020-03-27T04:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T05:22:56.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9a184886dbe25040e641e713d8ae702df27731c3","tid":1945424,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:49:30.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平回信給世衛組織總幹事譚德塞，讚賞世衛在譚德塞帶領下，積極推動對抗新型冠狀病毒疫情的國際合作，得到國際社會廣泛認可，中國將繼續堅定支持世衛發揮積極領導作用。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又說，當前中國疫情防控形勢持續向好，生產生活秩序加快恢復的態勢不斷鞏固和拓展，中國已經向包括世衛在內的國際組織以及80多個國家提供援助。中方將在力所能及範圍內，繼續支持國際社會抗擊疫情。"},{"pid":"1ece5a01f907156ac2b1e07a9cee5edbfa69a8e2","tid":1945424,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:52:37.000Z","msg":"習近平 go to hell"},{"pid":"a458ccce2e7bbbf006585ddb1b93ba9fba80eeca","tid":1945424,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:53:11.000Z","msg":"世衛工作Fact Check<br />\n再三強調唔會人傳人<br />\n市民無須戴口罩<br />\n轟歐美台限制中國人出入境<br />\n呼籲世人繼續去中國旅行及商貿<br />\n轟意大利爆大數"},{"pid":"169c1b9442687f9ec2daa3c48d074e131d9dd2e7","tid":1945424,"uid":6026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"互含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31997388e4e2f9c3b2207ae6c22c57abd4efb96a","tid":1945424,"uid":9542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"169c1b9442687f9ec2daa3c48d074e131d9dd2e7","tid":1945424,"uid":6026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"互含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"似係寫信感謝返自己多啲"},{"pid":"c87af673f4739a06bb0e26707b564e8fb2c6a840","tid":1945424,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31997388e4e2f9c3b2207ae6c22c57abd4efb96a","tid":1945424,"uid":9542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"169c1b9442687f9ec2daa3c48d074e131d9dd2e7","tid":1945424,"uid":6026,"like":3,"disli